  "html": "<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\">\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p>A <b>Broken Shell</b> is an <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Items\" title=\"Items\">Item</a> dropped by <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Slurtle\" title=\"Slurtle\">Slurtles</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Snurtle\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Snurtle\">Snurtles</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Slurtle_Mound\" title=\"Slurtle Mound\">Slurtle Mounds</a>, and <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crustashine\" title=\"Crustashine\">Crustashines</a> when killed or destroyed. Broken Shell can also be obtained by smashing <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Shell_Bells\" title=\"Shell Bells\">Shell Bells</a> with a hammer. \n</p><p>Broken Shell are required to craft <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Potted_Fern\" title=\"Potted Fern\">Potted Fern</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Shell_Beach_Turf\" title=\"Shell Beach Turf\">Shell Beach Turf</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Seed_Pack-It\" title=\"Seed Pack-It\">Seed Pack-it</a> and the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Bumpers#Shell_Bumper\" title=\"Bumpers\">Shell Bumper</a>.\n</p>\n<div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Usage\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Icon_Tools\" title=\"Icon Tools\"><img alt=\"Icon Tools.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Icon_Tools.png/32px-Icon_Tools.png?f672d4\" width=\"32\" height=\"39\"></a> Usage</span></h2>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Broken_Shell_(DST)\" title=\"Broken Shell (DST)\"><img alt=\"Broken Shell (DST).png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Broken_Shell_%28DST%29.png?855a5c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Foliage\" title=\"Foliage\"><img alt=\"Foliage.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Foliage.png?69c04c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>2</b></p></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Alchemy_Engine\" title=\"Alchemy Engine\"><img alt=\"Alchemy Engine.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Alchemy_Engine.png/42px-Alchemy_Engine.png?937c5f\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Potted_Fern\" title=\"Potted Fern\"><img alt=\"Potted Fern.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Potted_Fern.png?e4dc31\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Broken_Shell_(DST)\" title=\"Broken Shell (DST)\"><img alt=\"Broken Shell (DST).png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Broken_Shell_%28DST%29.png?855a5c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>2</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cut_Grass\" title=\"Cut Grass\"><img alt=\"Cut Grass.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Cut_Grass.png?90b46e\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>4</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Seeds\" title=\"Seeds\"><img alt=\"Seeds.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Seeds.png?3b6169\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>2</b></p></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Alchemy_Engine\" title=\"Alchemy Engine\"><img alt=\"Alchemy Engine.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Alchemy_Engine.png/42px-Alchemy_Engine.png?937c5f\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Seed_Pack-It\" title=\"Seed Pack-It\"><img alt=\"Seed Pack-It.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Seed_Pack-It.png?c9e