  "wikitext": "{{Navbutton/Separation}}\n{{Object Infobox\n|droppedBy = {{pic|30|Slurtle}}, {{pic|30|Snurtle}}, {{pic|30|Slurtle Mound}}<br>\n{{pic32|Sunken Chest}}, {{pic32|Baritone Shell Bell}}, {{pic32|Alto Shell Bell}}, {{pic32|Soprano Shell Bell}} {{pic|28|Crustashine}}\n|icon = Broken Shell (DST).png\n|image = Broken Shell Dropped (DST).png\n|stack = 40\n|spawnCode = \"slurtle_shellpieces\"}}\n{{Quotes\n|wilson = A puzzle with no solution.\n|willow = Heh. It broke.\n|wolfgang = Is broken.\n|wendy = Pieces of broken slurtle dreams.\n|wx78 = THEY DON'T FIT BACK TOGETHER\n|wickerbottom = Pieces of the broken.\n|woodie = I broke his home. I feel bad.\n|maxwell = They don't fit back together.\n|wagstaff = Perhaps they can be re-fused somehow.\n|wigfrid = They're smashed up gööd.\n|webber = We hit it a little too hard.\n|walani = Holding on to these doesn't even seem worth it.\n|warly = If only I had crazy glue.\n|woodlegs = I ain't one fer puzzlers.\n|wilba = BROKEN HOME O' SLIME BEASTIES\n|wormwood = Spiky Shell bits\n|wheeler = Pfft. Not even good as ammunition.\n|winona = Broke, but I might salvage something useful.\n|wortox = Shards of shell I do see here.\n|wurt = Aw, it broke!\n|walter = Sorry slurtle.\n|wanda = A handful of shattered shell bits.\n|choose = woodie}}\n\nA '''Broken Shell''' is an [[Items|Item]] dropped by [[Slurtle]]s, [[Snurtle]]s, [[Slurtle Mound]]s, and [[Crustashine|Crustashines]] when killed or destroyed. Broken Shell can also be obtained by smashing [[Shell Bells]] with a hammer. \n\nBroken Shell are required to craft [[Potted Fern]], [[Shell Beach Turf]], [[Seed Pack-It|Seed Pack-it]] and the [[Bumpers#Shell Bumper|Shell Bumper]].\n{{clear}}\n== {{pic|32|Icon Tools}} Usage ==\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Broken Shell (DST)\n|item2 = Foliage\n|count2 = 2\n|result = Potted Fern\n|Science 2 = yes}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Broken Shell (DST)\n|count1 = 2\n|item2 = Cut Grass\n|count2 = 4\n|item3 = Seeds\n|count3 = 2\n|result = Seed Pack-It\n|Science 2= yes}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Broken Shell (DST)\n|count1 = 3\n|item2 = Rope\n|count2 = 1\n|result = Shell Bumper Kit\n|resultcount = 1\n|tool = Think Tank}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Broken Shell (DST)\n|count1 = 1\n|item2 = Rocks\n|count2 = 1\n|result = Shell Beach Turf\n|resultcount = 4\n|tool = Blueprint (rare)}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Broken Shell (DST)\n|count1 = 1\n|item2 = Twigs\n|count2 = 1\n|tool = Crabby Hermit\n|result = Wind Charm\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Broken Shell (DST)\n|count1 = 3\n|item2 = Desert Stone\n|item3= Salt Crystals\n|count3 = 3\n|tool = Combriner\n|result = Portage Conch\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Broken Shell (DST)\n|count1 = 2\n|item2 = Rocks/DST\n|count2 = 3\n|item3 = Barnacles\n|count3 = 2\n|tool = Crabby Hermit\n|result = Pearl's Light Post\n}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Broken Shell (DST)\n|item2 = Ash\n|result = Spirit Vessel\n|character = Wendy\n|skill = Gravestones By Wendy\n}}\n\n\n{{Mob Dropped Items}}\n[[Category:Mob Dropped Items]]\n[[Category:Non-Flammable]]\n[[vi:Broken Shell]]"
